    "These findings validate that integrating drug sequence features with drug molecular graph structural features enhances the DDI prediction performance.Table 8 also presents the model's ACC, AUC, and F1 scores using the SGFE module, which achieves impressive values of 96.09%, 98.78%, and 96.15%, respectively.",
